Unofficial Translation by the Insurance Regulator of Cambodia

**KINGDOM OF CAMBODIA**
**NATIONAL – RELIGION – KING**

**MINISTRY OF ECONOMY AND FINANCE**
**No. 1038 MEF.BrK**

**PRAKAS**
**ON**
**PROCEDURE FOR RECEIVING AND RESOLVING**
**INSURANCE COMPLAINTS**

**Deputy Prime Minister, Minister of Economy and Finance**

- Having seen the Constitution of the Kingdom of Cambodia;
- Having seen the Royal Decree No. NS/RKT/0918/925 dated September 6, 2018, concerning the Nomination of the Royal Government of the Kingdom of Cambodia;
- Having seen the Royal Decree No. NS/RKT/0320/421 dated March 30, 2020, concerning the Appointment and Modification of the Composition of the Royal Government of Kingdom of Cambodia;
- Having seen the Royal Kram No. NS/RKT/0618/012 dated June 28, 2018, promulgating the Law on the Organization and Functioning of the Council of Ministers;
- Having seen the Royal Kram No. NS/RKT/0196/18 dated January 24, 1996, promulgating the Law on the Establishment of the Ministry of Economy and Finance;
- Having seen the Royal Kram No. NS/RKT/0814/021 dated August 4, 2014, promulgating the Law on Insurance;
- Having seen Sub-Decree No. 488 ANKr. BK dated October 16, 2013, concerning the Organization and Functioning of the Ministry of Economy and Finance;
- Having seen Sub-Decree No. 75 ANKr. BK dated May 25, 2017, concerning the Modification of Sub-Decree No. 488 dated October 16, 2013 on the Organization and Functioning of the Ministry of Economy and Finance;
- Having seen Sub-Decree No. 76 ANKr. BK dated June 13, 2018, concerning the Organization and Functioning of the Legal Council of the Ministry of Economy and Finance;
- Having seen Sub-Decree No. 106 ANKr. BK dated October 22, 2001, concerning the Insurance;
- Pursuant to the necessity of the Ministry of Economy and Finance

